  "description": "Transport yourself to sunny Italy with this protein-packed twist on the classic Caprese salad. You'll toss cherry tomatoes, cucumber and mozzarella in a tangy balsamic dressing before stirring in creamy white beans. Scatter with crispy croutons and drizzle with basil pesto to finish. 3 or more of your 5/day.\n",
